import React from 'react';
import {
    Box, 
    Button,
    Form,
    Header,
    TextInput
}from 'grommet';

const Signup = () => {
return(
    <>
    <Box justify="center" align="center">
        <Box backround="red" justify="center" align="center">
    <Header> Sign up </Header>
    <Form
    >
<TextInput 
placeholder="Username"
/>
<TextInput 
placeholder="Full Name"
/>

<TextInput 
placeholder="Email"
/>
<TextInput 
placeholder="password"
name="password"
htmlFor="password"
type="password"
/>
<TextInput 
placeholder="Confirm password"
name="password"
htmlFor="password"
type="password"
/>
</Form>
<Button label="Continue"/>
</Box>
</Box>
</>
)
};

export default Signup;
